        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\ntitle\n&lt;size:16&gt;&lt;b&gt;UC-05: Search and Filter Products - Activity Diagram&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/size&gt;\nend title\n\n|Buyer|\nstart\n\n:Type keyword in search bar and press Enter / click search icon;\n\n|System|\nif (Search bar empty?) then (yes)\n  :Display all approved listings (status &#39;Approved&#39;, stock &gt; 0) sorted by newest;\n  note right: Alternative Flow 1\nelse (no)\n  :Query product catalogue for approved listings matching keyword\n   (title, description, brand, model - case insensitive);\nendif\n\nif (No matching results found?) then (yes)\n  :Display &#39;No results for [keyword]&#39; and suggest popular categories;\n  note right: Alternative Flow 2\n  stop\nelse (no)\nendif\n\n:Display results in product grid (thumbnail, title, price, condition, seller rating);\n\n|Buyer|\n:Apply filters (Category, Brand, Price Range, Condition, Seller Rating, Availability);\n\n|System|\n:Update results in real-time based on selected filters;\n\n|Buyer|\n:Sort results (Relevance, Price Low/High, Newest, Seller Rating);\n\n|System|\n:Display updated sorted results;\n\n|Buyer|\n:Select a product to view its detail page;\n\nstop\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="U2y3R0-jDhVh8ACwDD4h-3">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
